column16: Shin-Soo Choo singles on a line drive to left fielder Eric Young.   Devin Mesoraco scores.    Derrick Robinson to 2nd.
Brandon Belt pops out to third baseman Josh Satin.
Gregor Blanco singles on a soft line drive to center fielder Juan Lagares.
Angel Pagan homers (4) on a fly ball to left center field.
Yusmeiro Petit strikes out swinging, catcher Anthony Recker to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Tony Abreu lines out to third baseman Josh Satin.
Pablo Sandoval grounds out, second baseman Daniel Murphy to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Denard Span grounds out, shortstop Ruben Tejada to first baseman Lucas Duda.
Anthony Rendon lines out to left fielder Eric Young.
Wilson Ramos grounds into a double play, shortstop Justin Turner to second baseman Wilmer Flores to first baseman Lucas Duda.   Adam LaRoche out at 2nd.
